        "content": "<p>Hi, in <code>Mathlib.Analysis.RCLike.Basic</code> we have this lemma:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">@[</span><span class=\"n\">rclike_simps</span><span class=\"kd\">]</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">theorem</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">zero_re'</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">re</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">K</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℝ</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">map_zero</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">re</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>I want to ask:<br>\n1) Why is <code>zero_re'</code> instead of <code>zero_re</code>?<br>\n2) Do we have version for <code>im</code>?</p>",
        "id": 519422684,
        "sender_full_name": "Iván Renison",
        "timestamp": 1747756714
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>It looks like <code>zero_re'</code> was added in <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib3/pull/4057\">mathlib3#4057</a> and <code>zero_re</code> was deleted in <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib3/pull/4824\">mathlib3#4824</a></p>",
        "id": 519427329,
        "sender_full_name": "Aaron Liu",
        "timestamp": 1747757992
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>This is misnamed anyway, it should be <code>re_zero</code></p>",
        "id": 519432859,
        "sender_full_name": "Jireh Loreaux",
        "timestamp": 1747759677
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=RCLike.zero_re#doc\">docs#RCLike.zero_re</a></p>",
