    {
        "content": "<p>Many lemmas about <code>RCLike</code> use <code>re</code> and <code>im</code> as suffixes, probably after <code>Complex</code> lemmas.</p>",
        "id": 519515463,
        "sender_full_name": "Yury G. Kudryashov",
        "timestamp": 1747799902
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Do you remember what was the outcome of the recent discussion about that?</p>",
